---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import PortfolioButtons from '@components/PortfolioButtons.astro'
import Testimonal from '@components/Testimonal.astro';
import CardIcon from '@components/CardIcon.astro';
import BigPortfolioButton from '@components/BigPortfolioButton.astro';
import PAGEDATA from '@data/index.json';
import SOCIALS from '@data/socials.json';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ImmersiveWorks from '@components/ImmersiveWorks.astro';

---

<Layout title="Niccolò Agnoletti - Developer, Designer, Illustrator">
	<main>
		<h1 class="uppercase font-extrabold leading-none text-2xl sm:text-[3.5rem] md:text-8xl p-4 m-auto">
			Ciao! Se sei qui immagino tu stia cercando<wbr/> il mio portfolio. Ecco qui:
		</h1>
		<ul class="flex flex-row flex-wrap mt-8 sm:mt-16 w-full overflow-x-clip px-3">
			<BigPortfolioButton 
			href="https://nicc-olo.com/portfolio/technical"
			title="Technical Stuff"
			src="/assets/images/punkwebdev.png"
			type="technical">
				<strong>FRONT END</strong> WEB<br/> <strong>DEVELOPEMENT.</strong>
			</BigPortfolioButton>			
			<BigPortfolioButton 
			href="https://nicc-olo.com/portfolio/creative"
			title="Creative Stuff"
			src="/assets/images/creativecat.png"
			type="creative">
				digital <strong>ILLUSTRATIONS,<br /> 
				GAMES, MAGAZINES.</strong>
			</BigPortfolioButton>
		</ul>
	</main>
	<section class="bg-accent px-4 py-24 mt-2 clip01">
		<h2 class="text-center font-extrabold uppercase text-3xl md:text-6xl text-pretty">O forse ti stai chiedendo<br>“scusa ma, chi c** sei?”</h2>
		<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row mt-8 md:gap-12 mx-auto max-w-5xl items-center">
			<img src="/assets/images/weirdnic.png" height="200px" width="200px" alt="" class="w-full max-w-md h-auto" />
			<div class="drop-shadow-md">
				<div class="bg-white/50 p-8 sm:p-12 w-fit h-fit text-xl font-cursive rotate-1" style="clip-path: polygon(18% 1%, 36% 0, 49% 2%, 55% 1%, 88% 2%, 99% 1%, 100% 42%, 99% 55%, 100% 76%, 99% 88%, 99% 98%, 82% 100%, 36% 99%, 17% 100%, 4% 98%, 1% 91%, 1% 55%, 0% 44%, 1% 29%, 1% 2%);">
					<p> Mi presento: </p>
					<p class="mt-2">
						Mi chiamo Niccolò Agnoletti (con due C) e sono uno <strong>sviluppatore web</strong>. Mi occupo principalmente di progettazione di siti web per il marketing.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-2">
						Ogni tanto faccio anche <a href="https://www.dafont.com/it/blazardsky.d6835" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">dei font (tipo questo)</a> e illustrazioni digitali o grafiche per <a href="/projects">vari progetti.</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>			
	</section>
	<PortfolioButtons />
	<section class="bg-foreground text-background px-4 py-24 clip01">
		<h2 class="text-center font-light uppercase text-3xl md:text-6xl mt-24">
			No? va beh, allora<br/> continua a scrollare 
		</h2>
		<h3 class="text-center font-extrabold uppercase text-2xl md:text-5xl mt-44">
			1. Perché lavorare con me :)
		</h3>
		<ul class="group list-none p-2">
			{
				PAGEDATA.testimonials.map(testimonial => (
				  <Testimonal 
				  	id={testimonial.id}
					name={testimonial.by} 
					role={testimonial.role}
					body={testimonial.body}
					src={testimonial.img}
					link={testimonial.link}
				  />
				))
			}
		</ul>
		<h4 class="text-center font-extrabold uppercase text-xl md:text-4xl mt-36">
			I miei punti di forza
		</h4>
		<ul class="my-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row max-w-5xl mx-auto gap-8">
			<CardIcon title="Problem solving" body="Sono abituato a lavorare in autonomia e con più gradi di responsabilità, trovando soluzioni creative ai problemi posti" icon="problemsolving" />			
			<CardIcon title="Multidisciplinarietà" body="Ho conoscenze trasversali per cui posso fare “da ponte” tra il team di sviluppo e il team di design ed essere versatile in progetti più piccoli"  icon="multidisciplinare" />
			<CardIcon title="Esperienza mista" body="Ho lavorato sia con agenzie e aziende che direttamente con clienti e per varie tipologie di progetto." icon="esperienzamista" />
		</ul>
	</section>
	<section class="px-4 py-24">
		<h3 class="text-center font-extrabold uppercase text-2xl md:text-5xl mt-36">
			2. Le mie competenze
		</h3>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl my-12">
			<span class="bg-technical rounded-md p-1 uppercase font-bold">TECH</span>
			<h4 class="mt-1 uppercase text-3xl">
				Progettazione e sviluppo di <strong>siti web</strong> completa sia come <strong>codice</strong> che come <strong>ui/ux</strong>.
			</h4>
			<p class="font-cursive text-lg text-balance">Conosco bene CSS, SASS, JS, REACT, HTML, oltre a Python e PHP. I miei framework preferiti in ambito js sono NextJS e Astro. Ho una certa esperienza con WordPress e Shopify (sia in ambito “code” che “no-code”) ma solitamente uso Sanity come CMS headless per creare soluzioni totalmente custom. <wbr />Cerco di creare sempre esperienze web, adattabili, responsive accessibili (a11y/wcag) e ben strutturate (semantic html).</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl my-12">
			<span class="bg-creative rounded-md p-1 uppercase font-bold">Creative</span>
			<h4 class="mt-1 uppercase text-3xl">
				Ideazione e realizzazione di <strong>grafiche</strong> e <strong>illustrazioni</strong> per la stampa e per il digitale.
			</h4>
			<p class="font-cursive text-lg text-balance">Conosco bene Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign e in generale i programmi Adobe. Ultimamente sto imparando ad usare la suite Affinity by Serif. Uso spesso anche Procreate e Figma. I miei ambiti preferiti per cui creare artwork sono abbigliamento, magazine e libri, album musicali. Ho una certa esperienza anche con varie AI generative che ho sperimentato fin dai loro primi esordi.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl my-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row">
			<p class="uppercase opacity-70">
				Se ti interessa sapere altro puoi guardare questa <a href="/skills" class="underline">paginetta delle competenze</a> oppure inviarmi un messaggio su <a href={SOCIALS[1].link} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">LinkedIn.</a> &UpperRightArrow;
			</p>
			<Image src="/assets/images/fiorellini.png" alt="due fiorellini con una faccia sorridente" height="190" width="190" />
		</div>
		<Image class="hidden md:block w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto" src="/assets/images/friends_garden.png" alt="Illustrazione dei vari strumenti che uso per lavorare con le gambe e una faccia per renderli buffi" height="777" width="1234" />
	</section>
	<!--section class="px-4 py-36">
		<h3 class="text-center font-extrabold uppercase text-5xl">
			3. PS: Ho anche delle certificazioni
		</h3>
		<ul class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid grid-flow-row sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 md:gap-9 my-12 text-center">
			<li class="p-2 border-foreground border rounded-md">
				<h4 class="block uppercase font-extrabold text-3xl leading-none">E-Design<br/>Illustrazione</h4>
				<p class="mt-2 font-cursive text-xs">Accademia Nemo</p>
			</li>
			<li class="p-2 border-foreground border rounded-md">
				<h4 class="block uppercase font-extrabold text-3xl leading-none">Joy of<br/>React</h4>
				<p class="mt-2 font-cursive text-xs">Josh W. Comeau</p>
			</li>
			<li class="p-2 border-foreground border rounded-md sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
				<h4 class="block uppercase font-extrabold text-3xl leading-none">Landing Page<br/>Academy</h4>
				<p class="mt-2 font-cursive text-xs">Erik D. Kennedy</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section -->

	<ImmersiveWorks />

	<PortfolioButtons before_title="giunti fin qui" />
	
	<section>

		<svg width="63" height="607" viewBox="0 0 63 607" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mx-auto">
			<g clip-path="url(#clip0_168_60)">
			<path class="n__path" d="M55.2601 10.8709C48.1327 10.5543 27.6833 4.83461 22.6046 12.8661C15.974 23.352 46.2078 29.3093 48.9102 30.1423C58.4587 33.0856 67.4054 36.8907 54.7898 45.3054C51.8011 47.299 15.2807 71.7295 26.012 76.2431C30.9691 78.3281 38.5593 76.9237 42.9034 80.4389C50.606 86.6719 35.4798 119.716 33.5747 126.539C30.4856 137.604 28.1467 143.234 35.6361 148.682C39.9273 151.804 31.4203 160.638 30.0056 163.679C24.5828 175.334 55.8257 176.181 45.9527 187.645C39.9597 194.603 32.855 199.288 30.6523 210.222C27.7854 224.455 40.1686 234.928 44.8365 245.566C51.741 261.302 38.1758 259.747 31.1193 265.286C20.1712 273.878 39.9539 309.901 42.7572 319.209C47.154 333.806 45.8972 333.663 39.7063 343.192C36.7612 347.725 39.7402 353.677 40.9577 358.236C42.2652 363.13 42.4845 366.25 39.7511 370.5C39.1367 371.455 35.2944 375.036 35.6992 376.78C36.5296 380.357 41.452 384.602 43.1761 387.277C48.1482 394.99 48.8484 399.768 43.9774 407.985C40.8707 413.227 36.5718 418.319 35.022 424.815C33.9081 429.485 36.0345 433.282 36.703 437.639C37.5581 443.211 35.465 447.837 33.5207 452.658C30.6692 459.728 31.5705 459.806 35.5435 465.238C47.9151 482.153 45.7311 498.696 43.5098 519.859C40.7422 546.226 40.6646 572.994 37.4676 599.269" stroke="#222222" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
			</g>
			<defs>
			<clipPath id="clip0_168_60">
			<rect width="63" height="607" fill="white"/>
			</clipPath>
			</defs>
		</svg>
			
		<h5 class="uppercase font-extrabold text-center">Oppure vuoi contattarmi?</h5>
		<img src="/assets/images/scimmietta.png" alt="una specie di scimmietta attaccata a una freccia che indica verso il basso" class="mx-auto max-w-64" height="254" width="375" />
		<div class="mt-24 md:mt-64 mx-auto max-w-[94vw] md:max-w-3xl text-2xl md:text-5xl relative" id="cta_lavoro">
			<p class="uppercase font-extrabold text-left p-8 md:px-12 md:pt-12 pb-20 mb-28 bg-midground -rotate-2 has-[a:hover]:rotate-2 will-change-transform transition-transform ease-out" style="clip-path: polygon(2% 1%, 0% 5%, 12% 2%, 18% 0%, 25% 1%, 32% 0%, 38% 2%, 51% 2%, 48% 0%, 59% 0%, 56% 1%, 69% 1%, 67% 0%, 80% 0%, 83% 1%, 87% 0%, 91% 2%, 94% 1%, 99% 0%, 100% 8%, 100% 14%, 99% 19%, 100% 24%, 99% 30%, 100% 36%, 100% 49%, 98% 47%, 100% 57%, 100% 64%, 99% 66%, 100% 71%, 98% 84%, 100% 87%, 100% 95%, 98% 100%, 80% 100%, 86% 99%, 69% 99%, 64% 100%, 55% 99%, 50% 100%, 39% 94%, 43% 100%, 36% 99%, 29% 100%, 24% 98%, 15% 100%, 9% 100%, 4% 100%, 1% 98%, 5% 90%, 1% 83%, 2% 69%, 0% 62%, 1% 44%, 0% 32%, 2% 23%, 0% 12%, 4% 12%, 0% 4%);">sono disponibile a lavorare da remoto in Europa e nel mondo: <a href="mailto:ciao@nicc-olo.com" class="underline">contattami</a></p>
			<svg class="absolute -bottom-28 left-[8ch]" width="117" height="167" viewBox="0 0 117 167" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
				<path d="M48.1235 3.05025C54.8442 16.5497 61.8563 29.937 68.2074 43.6155C74.4595 57.0808 77.335 71.0454 78.4731 86.0738C79.3926 98.2164 79.4842 107.647 78.4368 119.934C77.1724 134.766 72.8408 148.483 69.584 163.076" stroke="#222222" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
				<path d="M68.9448 163.571C66.8524 159.369 64.7601 155.166 62.6677 150.963C61.5196 148.657 60.6063 146.152 58.4967 144.507" stroke="#222222" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
				<path d="M69.656 164.36C73.0322 162.679 76.0629 161.169 78.9082 158.675C82.0364 155.933 84.6013 152.79 87.197 149.632" stroke="#222222" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
				</svg>
		</div>
		<p class="font-cursive max-w-sm mx-auto px-8 text-pretty text-center">In particolare per progetti editoriali o se rappresenti uno studio creativo in cerca di collaboratori. <wbr/>Se invece hai bisogno di esperti di marketing e comunicazione, <a href="mailto:info@kipoproduzioni.it" class="underline">scrivi a Kìpo</a></p>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .n__path {
	stroke-dasharray: 810;
	stroke-dashoffset: 815;
	animation: dash 6s linear;
  }
</style>

<script>
	import { gsap } from "gsap";
	import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";
	gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger) ;
	
	gsap.to('.n__path', {
		strokeDashoffset: 0,
		duration: 3,
		ease: 'ease',
		scrollTrigger: '.n__path',
	});

	gsap.fromTo('#cta_lavoro', {
		scale: 0.8,
		opacity: 0.75,
		rotate: "-2deg",
	}, {
		scale: 1,
		opacity: 1,
		rotate: 0,
		delay: 0.5,
		duration: 0.35,
		ease: 'ease',
		scrollTrigger: '#cta_lavoro'
	} );
</script>